{"tid":1230384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急","createTime":"2019-06-16T07:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T07:36:14.000Z","uid":194894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3e83e6749ee476758938a3d603e3df303bc13b","tid":1230384,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"油塘三家村有碼頭去西灣河碼頭<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想係油塘地鐵白等，可以坐船去西灣河再轉地鐵。<br />\n<br />\n係就係麻煩啲，不過依家已經無野可以阻到香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSdyhbv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSdyhbv.png&h=838ecf15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"357b75a3fd9bf50d23918b6907c2df78aedef922","tid":1230384,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fad34db68b184aaaa685d3d64a6c0f3b5a4c9c8","tid":1230384,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:30